description: Further intelligence failings emerge prompting the Austrian city's anti-terror head to step aside.
title: Vienna shooting: Anti-terror chief suspended over intelligence bungle
title_page: Vienna shooting: Anti-terror chief suspended over intelligence bungle - BBC News
maintext: Although they were not seen as suspects in the shooting itself, two of the four are thought to have met the attacker in Vienna in July and were described in Germany as "part of the Islamist scene".
